snippet.title: Massive Monster Dash update – Barry is back!
snippet.description:
▶︎ Click to Subscribe: http://bit.ly/HalfbrickYTSubscribe

▶︎ 🔥 Download the App: https://jetpackjoyride.page.link/YouTubeJetpack

Follow us on Social Media: 
Twitter: @Halfbrick
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/halfbrick/

Welcome to the new evolution of Monster Dash, part of the legendary Barry Steakfries Trilogy along with Jetpack Joyride and Age of Zombies! With online leaderboards, majestic medals and a new leveling system, this is the definitive version of Monster Dash and one of the greatest runner games ever made. Do the Dash. Do the Monster Dash!
